    stimulus: `Disability rights advocate: Some critics argue that requiring businesses to install wheelchair ramps and accessible restrooms imposes an unreasonable financial burden. But consider: we do not regard fire exits and sprinkler systems as unreasonable burdens, even though they too require significant investment. Both types of requirements serve the fundamental purpose of ensuring that buildings are safe and usable for all members of the public.`,
