    stimulus: `A small island nation facing rising sea levels due to climate change has called on industrialized countries to provide financial assistance for relocation and infrastructure adaptation. The industrialized countries have historically produced the vast majority of the greenhouse gas emissions responsible for climate change, while the island nation has contributed negligibly to global emissions.`,
