    stimulus: `A technology commentator argues that artificial intelligence systems will never be capable of genuine creativity because every output an AI produces is ultimately derived from patterns in its training data. The commentator notes that even the most impressive AI-generated artworks are recombinations of elements from human-created works the system was trained on.`,
