    stimulus: `A school board member argues that the district's new digital textbook program must be effective at improving student learning because a survey of teachers in the district found that 80 percent rated the digital textbooks as "excellent" or "very good." The board member points out that teachers are the professionals best positioned to evaluate educational materials.`,
